title: PMDG  777-200LRF
description:
Hello my friends,

This is the PMDG 777 as recently released!!
This is the first upload it's not been cracked since i've bought it.

Let me give the cracker a little headstart, the licening is done by an external application called LC Certificate if i remember correctly,
it only asks for a serial key when selecting this beauty from the menu. that's the activation part of it.

I've been downloading pmdg's software for quite a while now, decided to start supporting them. but also you guys helped me out numerous times so let me help you out a bit.

Have fun!
